1. *Stav* nam je bio jasan. (The stance was clear to us.) 
2. Ona je imala svoj *stav* o tome. (She had her own stance on that.)
3. Pogledao sam svoj *stav* u odnosu na to. (I looked at my stance in relation to that.)
4. On je promenio *stav* o stvari. (He changed his stance on the matter.)
5. Mi smo zauzeli *stav* da nešto nećemo učiniti. (We took the stance that we wouldn't do something.)
6. Oni su imali svoj *stav* u vezi sa tim. (They had their own stance regarding that.)
7. Ona je promenila svoj *stav*. (She changed her stance.)
8. Oni su zadržali svoj *stav*. (They maintained their stance.)